author: The Current
description:
Digital Producer Luke Taylor talks about the impact The Current has had on radio in the Twin Cities over the last 20 years.

We’re celebrating The Current’s 20th Anniversary all year long with the music and people that made this unique Minnesota music community possible. 

Find more at thecurrent.org/anniversary
